mfaz.01.Rd

A sample MUAC screening data from an anonymized setting

Usage

mfaz.01

Format

A tibble with 661 rows and 4 columns.

VariableDescription
sexSex, "m" = boys, "f" = girls
monthscalculated age in months with two decimal places
edemaEdema, "n" = no, "y" = yes
muacMid-upper arm circumference (mm)

Source

Anonymous
